data.description:
Opportunity Zone! Horse Privileges! This residence at one time was converted into a really nice duplex with Unit #1 being a 3 Bedroom, 1 bath. Unit #2 is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath. A few years back the duplex was made back into a residence. **This can easily be converted back to a duplex with one wall. A family member used to have a Diesel Truck Business in the back of the property where the shop/office is located. There is vehicle entry from the back of the property as well and plenty of parking. Owner will entertain all offers. entrepreneurial ventures or additional income streams.

Convenience is also guaranteed with vehicle entry available from the rear of the property and ample parking spaces provided on-site.

Considering all these attractive features and potential uses, the owner is open to entertaining all offers. This presents an excellent chance for discerning buyers or investors looking to make their mark in this sought-after location.
